text: "I Feel It Coming" is a 2016 song by Canadian singer the Weeknd and is the third single from his third studio album Starboy. The song features French duo Daft Punk. It topped the single charts in France. It also went to the top 10 in Argentina, Australia, Belgium, Canada, the Czech Republic, Denmark, Ecuador, Hungary, Ireland, Israel, Lebanon, Mexico, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Slovakia, Spain, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom and the United States. == References == Category:2016 songs Category:The Weeknd songs Category:Daft Punk songs
title: I Feel It Coming
